cc:Work.dc:title: MiAIRR data standard elements

cc:Agent.dc:title: Corey Watson, Syed Ahmad Chan Bukhari, Christian Busse

cc:Work.dc:description: This figure shows the sets, subsets and individual items of the MiAIRR (minimal information about adaptive immune receptor repertoires) standard. It further includes the mapping of the NCBI implementation of the standard, the respective target repositories for the items are depicted with a solid line.
